==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Resolvedly
<hw>Re*solv"ed*ly</hw> <pr>(r?z?lv"?d-l?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>So as to resolve or clear up difficulties;
clearly.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Of that, and all the progress, more or less,⟦br⟧
<qex>Resolvedly</qex> more leisure shall express.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Resolutely; decidedly; firmly.</def>
<rj><au>Grew.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resolvedness</ent>⟦br⟧
